00:11.512 --> 00:13.263
[horse whinnies]

00:18.101 --> 00:20.521
‐ I've got to find Mom and Dad!

00:20.521 --> 00:22.856
‐ Princess Blossom, wait!

00:24.316 --> 00:26.151
‐ Mom?! Daddy?

00:26.151 --> 00:27.736
