00:28.987 --> 00:31.657
‐ Princess, please, it's not safe.

00:31.657 --> 00:33.408
‐ Umm, no shit, Patrick.

00:33.408 --> 00:36.495
That guy has an axe
through his fucking face.

00:36.495 --> 00:37.955
‐ We need to get you away from here.

00:37.955 --> 00:40.582
‐ I wonder if before he died,
he had time to think,

00:40.582 --> 00:43.335
"Oh, fuck, there's an axe in my face."

00:43.335 --> 00:45.087
