00:47.339 --> 00:48.924
‐ Huh?
‐ What the?

00:48.924 --> 00:51.218
‐ Blossom!
‐ My sweet baby!

00:51.218 --> 00:53.136
‐ Mommy! Daddy!

00:53.136 --> 00:54.680
