01:04.356 --> 01:06.191
Pipe down unless you can help me.

01:06.191 --> 01:09.361
"Greetings for an elderly dog,"
11 letters.

01:09.361 --> 01:11.321
‐ You old bitch!

01:11.321 --> 01:14.616
‐ I was hoping you died up here
and nobody told me.

01:14.616 --> 01:18.453
‐ Hello, brother dear.
Look who got overthrown.

01:18.453 --> 01:21.331
