and being ugly gave her a motive.

02:48.836 --> 02:51.547
‐ I'm not ugly.
I just wear glasses.

02:55.092 --> 02:56.218
‐ Damn, girl.

02:59.429 --> 03:00.806
‐ Holy shit. Holy shit...

03:00.806 --> 03:02.182
