03:02.182 --> 03:04.184
‐ You guys, help me!

03:05.853 --> 03:07.062
‐ What do we do now?

03:07.062 --> 03:09.523
‐ We stay in here until it's over.

03:09.523 --> 03:11.233
‐ What about Princess Blossom?

03:11.233 --> 03:13.402
‐ Probably dead. [softly] I hope.

03:13.402 --> 03:15.112
‐ But she's our friend. Hello.

03:15.112 --> 03:16.780
